  address     =	{Adelaide, Australia},
  abstract    =	{ This paper investigates the long-lived TCP bulk throughput
		over the CDMA 1x EV-DO service that provides high-speed
		\always on" Internet connectivity in a wide-area mobile
		environment. Although the peak rates of downlink/uplink are
